description: Whether you’re a bunch of Kansas City yuppies or hippies, as long as you’re hungry, you’re welcome at Whippy’s American Classics!This retro restaurant on wheels is whipping up this country’s classic cuisine, including juicy burgers, hot and salty fries, super fun funnel cake, and so much more. If you’re super cool and love to live it up old school, you’ve got to visit this timeless truck. With taste and quality this far out, you can’t help but shout "Yipee!" for Whippy’s!
name: Whippy's American Classics
